# How to implement the project

Rules for implementing the project.

<rule>
name: how_to_implement
description: Standards and procedures for implementing the project

actions:
  - type: execute
    message: |
      When working on the project:

      1. Always read the Requirements.md file to understand the project requirements
      2. Never modify the Requirements.md file
      3. Always write unit tests for the code you write
      4. Always run the unit tests after each complete change you make
      5. Always build the project after each complete change you make
      6. After every change, make sure the README.md file is updated to include a basic overview of the changes and the correct way to build and run the project.


